11 An Act relating to roads and bridges; amending 69
O.S. 2021, Section 1521, as amended by Section 1,
12 Chapter 460, O.S.L. 2025 (69 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
1521), which relates to the Rebuilding Oklahoma
13 Access and Driver Safety Fund; modifying certain
apportionment for certain fiscal years; updating
14 statutory language; providing an effective date; and
declaring an emergency.
