15 prescribed by subparagraph a of this paragraph, shall
16 be apportioned before any other amount is apportioned
17 pursuant to Section 2352 of Title 68 of the Oklahoma
18 Statutes, plus
19 c. an additional amount that is required in order for the
20 total apportionment to the Rebuilding Oklahoma Access
21 and Driver Safety Fund from all sources for such
22 fiscal year to equal:
